    "One of the future tasks is promoting the machine learning theoretical research [435] on foundational models.",
    "Analyzing the machine learning properties of foundational models will reveal their unique patterns, providing the researchers with insights to design reasonable models and enhance the research and development efficiency.",
    "However, the existing theory of representation, optimization, or generalization is unable for HFMs, because their enormous parameters and data amount extremely exceed the ideal settings for these theories [436].",
